# Routing and Handoffs

- Pick one bounded next move before implementation.
- Classify mutation budget: low / medium / high.
- Low mutation: single practical path.
- Medium/high mutation: safe path + mutation path + recommended path.
- Keep output sequence-aware and anti-drift.

# Handoff Minimum

- goal and scope
- mutation budget
- files touched
- validation status
- risks
- one next bounded follow-up

